# Testing

Run: `pnpm test` (`node --test tests/`).

## Conventions

- Use `node:test` and `node:assert/strict`
- HTML fixtures in `tests/fixtures/` — never fetch live sites in unit tests
- Plugin loader tests: call `clearPluginCache()` in `beforeEach`
- Test scrapers in isolation; test plugin contract (id, required methods)
- Follow patterns in `tests/plugins/centralnovel.test.js` and `tests/plugins/loader.test.js`

## Plugin tests checklist

1. `parseSeriesPage` with fixture HTML → expected volume keys and cap IDs
2. Helper functions (URL extraction, etc.) with edge cases
3. Plugin exports valid `SourcePlugin` shape

## After adding a plugin

Ensure `discoverPlugins()` finds it (folder name === id, has `index.js`).
